title: Alford's INT return lifts Falcons past Redskins 25-19 in OT
text:
> Top News Alford's INT return lifts Falcons past Redskins 25-19 in OT RETRANSMISSION TO CORRECT DAY TO SUNDAY - Atlanta Falcons cornerback Robert Alford intercepts Washington Redskins quarterback Kirk Cousins during overtime and returns the ball for the game winning touchdown in an NFL football game, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015 in Atlanta.
